{"type":null,"faqId":45469,"title":"华为盒子亮度调暗后看不清屏幕，如何调亮？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.3048611in;}\n.p1{text-indent:-0.2951389in;margin-left:1.4763889in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">1.  </span><span>按1次</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=165085\" style=\"width:0.35416666in;height:0.3326389in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>按键，按8次右键，按1次下键，按3次右键，按1次 OK 键，按1次下键，按1次 OK 键。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">2.  </span><span>按住左键不放，屏幕会逐渐变亮。屏幕变亮后，可以看到亮度调节的按钮。按左右方向键，可将屏幕调亮或调暗。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">3.  </span><span>按1次返回键，按1次下键，按1次OK键。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">4.  </span><span>按住左键不放，屏幕显示效果会逐渐恢复正常。屏幕恢复正常后，可以看到对比度调节的按钮。按左右方向键，可将屏幕调亮或调暗。</span>\n</p>\n<br>\n<p  ></p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":247,"faqType":"显示","useful":1,"unUseful":1,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"989","faqTypeCode":"Media_Device-Display","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1442557785000,"seriesProductName":"MediaQ M330","visitedTimes":12,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"亮度,调亮","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}